V nsledujic loze jsem pracoval na rozpoznn kontury, obrysu, roh a tit pidan kostky. Rozpoznvan jsem eil tak e jsem nael spodn a horn mez spektrumu barvy kostky a pak z toho udlal threshold. Jeliko je barva kostky velice podobn jinm barvm v pozad, nepodailo se mi vechno vyet hladce a dokonal.

Na rozpoznn barvy kostky jsem nael kousek kdu a nsledn ho pravil. V nm se daji pravovat minimln a maximln hodnoty HSV (hue, saturation, value) na urenm obrzku dokud se nenleznou poadovany hodnoty.

Funkce kter vraci poet kontur (vdy jedna, jen pro kontrolu), a obrzek kontury, co je kontura kostky.

In [10]:
def detect_shape(image_url, bg_url):
    img = cv2.imread(image_url)
    bg = cv2.imread(bg_url)
    
    hsv_img = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2HSV)
    hsv_bg = cv2.cvtColor(bg, cv2.COLOR_BGR2HSV)
    
    lower_color = np.array([0, 42, 0])
    upper_color = np.array([30,255,255])
    
    mask_img = cv2.inRange(hsv_img, lower_color, upper_color)
    mask_bg = cv2.inRange(hsv_bg, lower_color, upper_color)
    
    subtracted_img = cv2.subtract(mask_img, mask_bg)
    
    ret, img_threshold = cv2.threshold(subtracted_img, 120, 255, cv2.THRESH_BINARY)
    
    contours, hierarchy = cv2.findContours(subtracted_img, cv2.RETR_TREE, cv2.CHAIN_APPROX_SIMPLE)
    contours_s = []
    for contour in contours:
        contour_area = cv2.contourArea(contour)
        if contour_area > 1500:
            contours_s.append(contour)
    return [contours_s, img_threshold]

Funkce kter vrac obrazek s nakreslenm obloukem a titm kontury(kostky).

In [11]:
def detect_arc_center(original_image, contours):
    epsilon = 0.1*cv2.arcLength(contours,True)
    ctr_aprx = cv2.approxPolyDP(contours,epsilon,True)
    height, width, channels = original_image.shape
    im2 = Image.new('RGBA', (width, height), (0, 0, 0, 255)) 
    draw2 = ImageDraw.Draw(im2)
    for i in range(len(ctr_aprx)):
        if (i == (len(ctr_aprx)-1)):
            draw2.line((ctr_aprx[i][0][0], ctr_aprx[i][0][1], ctr_aprx[0][0][0], ctr_aprx[0][0][1]), fill=128, width=3)
        else:
            draw2.line((ctr_aprx[i][0][0], ctr_aprx[i][0][1], ctr_aprx[i+1][0][0], ctr_aprx[i+1][0][1]), fill=128, width=3)
    points = detect_mass_center(contours)
    draw2.line((points[0], points[1], (points[0]-1), (points[1]-1)), fill=128, width=4)
    return im2

Funkce kter vrac body rohu kostky. Jeliko je epsilon rovno 0,1 tak se vdy vrat 4 aproximan hodnoty, hodnoty jsou body kter by mli co nejlep odhadnout obrys kostky. Tyhle 4 body uvauj za rohy kostky.

In [12]:
def detect_corners(contours):
    corners = []
    epsilon = 0.1*cv2.arcLength(contours,True)
    ctr_aprx = cv2.approxPolyDP(contours,epsilon,True)
    for i in range(len(ctr_aprx)):
        corners.append(ctr_aprx[i][0])
    return corners

Funkce kter vrac souadnice x a y tit kontury.

In [13]:
def detect_mass_center(contours):
    center_points = []
    M = cv2.moments(contours)
    cX = int(M["m10"] / M["m00"])
    cY = int(M["m01"] / M["m00"])
    center_points.append(cX)
    center_points.append(cY)
    return center_points

    "v3" : "verze 3"
}

pozadi_cesta = 'Input_bg\\bg.jpg'
cesta_zz = r'Input'
soubory = next(os.walk(cesta_zz))[2]

poradi = 0;
for i in soubory:
    poradi = poradi + 1
    c = cesta_zz + '\\' + i
    a, b = detect_shape(c, pozadi_cesta)
    
    c_1 = c.split("\\")
    c_2 = c_1[1].split(".")
    rozklad = c_2[0].split("_")
    
    if len(a) == 1:
        print(str(poradi) + ". Kostka s potem " + preklad[rozklad[0]] + " " + verze[rozklad[1]] + ": True")
    else:
        print(str(poradi) + ". Kostka s potem " + preklad[rozklad[0]] + " " + verze[rozklad[1]] + ": False")
